title: WBFF Worlds Toronto 2016
description:
World Beauty Fitness & Fashion Inc. Worlds - Toronto 2016
Day 1 of 2 - Friday, August 26th
Day 2 of 2 - Saturday, August 27th

Resolution: 1280x720
Codec: H.264
Container: MKV

Unfortunately, the volume is very inconsistent during the red carpet commentary and interviews as the mics seem to be mixed in at different levels.
Considering that I paid $55 USD for pay-per-view, this is quite ridiculous.
Therefore, I think it's more than fair that I share this with you all! ;)
